OL,6,FThames Water is sitting in the
OL,7,Fdeparture lounge waiting to find out
OL,8,Fit's destined for bright new horizons
OL,9,For the arms of the taxpayer.
OL,11,FThe company is beset by uncertainty,
OL,12,Fperforming poorly and therefore a
OL,13,Fregular target of both political flak
OL,14,Fand public fury.
OL,16,FWho'd want to manage a company like
OL,17,FThames?
