OL,6,FOn one level, you can understand the
OL,7,Flogic of promising 21 senior managers
OL,8,Fat Thames bonuses totalling #15.7
OL,9,Fmillion, just for hanging on in there
OL,10,Funtil June 2026.
OL,12,FYou can also understand why the
OL,13,Fpayouts, which are not linked to
OL,14,Fperformance, are being characterised
OL,15,Fas rewarding something that looks a
OL,16,Flot like failure.
