OL,3,CThames Water opts not to claw-back
OL,4,C#2.5m of bonuses
OL,6,FThe Management Retention Plan (MRP) is
OL,7,Ftargeted at a "small number of
OL,8,Findividuals considered to be critical
OL,9,Fto both the Company's restructuring
OL,10,Fprocess and ongoing operational
OL,11,Fimprovement," explains Sir Adrian
OL,12,FMontague, Thames' chairman.
OL,14,FHis letter to the Environment Select
OL,15,FCommittee reveals that eight members
OL,16,Fof the firm's leadership team of 40
OL,17,Fresigned in the year to March 2025,
OL,18,Fand that those who remain are
OL,19,F"regularly" approached with offers to
OL,20,Fjump ship.
