OL,3,CThames Water opts not to claw-back
OL,4,C#2.5m of bonuses
OL,6,FIn an attempt to hold onto "the
OL,7,Fhighest calibre of talent," Thames
OL,8,FWater paid nearly #2.5 million to its
OL,9,Fsenior managers on April 21.
OL,11,FThe managers, who are all paid
OL,12,Fsalaries of between #100,000 and
OL,13,F#500,000, are due to receive the same
OL,14,Famount again in December and a further
OL,15,F#10.8 million next June.
OL,17,FThe company paused its MRP in May
OL,18,Fafter the government expressed
OL,19,Fdisapproval.
