OL,3,CThames Water opts not to claw-back
OL,4,C#2.5m of bonuses
OL,6,FMontague says the board does not
OL,7,Fintend to recover the bonuses that
OL,8,Fhave been paid to date.
OL,10,FHe adds that the MRP "was and remains
OL,11,Fpaused" pending a decision by OFWAT on
OL,12,Fwhether it should be allowed to
OL,13,Fcontinue.
OL,15,FThames is financing the bonuses using
OL,16,Fmoney from an emergency loan of #3
OL,17,Fbillion which is intended to keep the
OL,18,Ffirm afloat while its future is
OL,19,Fdecided.
