OL,3,CThames Water opts not to claw-back
OL,4,C#2.5m of bonuses
OL,6,FIn his letter to MPs, the chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, David Black, said he was
OL,8,F"disappointed at the lack of
OL,9,Ftransparency... at a time when
OL,10,Fremuneration in the water sector is
OL,11,Funder significant public scrutiny".
OL,13,FThe government had already moved to
OL,14,Fblock the bonuses paid the executives
OL,15,Fat six water companies, including
OL,16,FThames, in 2024/25 but the rules only
OL,17,Fextend to chief executives, chief
OL,18,Ffinancial officer and chairs.
